    {
      "id": "1944750c-f3ba-80b6-97a1-ca10d2614296",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Different classifiers were used, and predictions at the end of the first semester outperformed the beginning of the course. Moreover, Logistic Regression was good enough as a baseline, but was outperformed by other ML techniques.",
